{"tid":627526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[RIP]英調查最受尊敬名人榜 成龍拿第3 擠下習近平(第4)","createTime":"2018-04-13T04:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T06:56:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"560c204ca0af2d81b2e9b1270c3b8341a0ddc1c4","tid":627526,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/121/5aceb9c5d035f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F121%2F5aceb9c5d035f.jpg&h=5c4b52c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誰是世界上最受尊敬的人？英國1份民調出爐，微軟創辦人比爾．蓋茲（Bill Gates）與好萊塢女星安潔莉娜裘莉（Angelina Jolie）分居男女榜首，而男性的第2名是美國前總統歐巴馬（Barack Obama），第3名則由香港演員成龍勝出，又把中國國家主席習近平踩了下去。<br />\n<br />\n英國民意調查機構YouGov公布最新民調，2018世界最受尊敬男士前5名，分別是比蓋茲、歐巴馬、成龍、習近平與中國商人馬雲入選。俄羅斯強人總統普亭（Vladimie Putin）跌出前5名，只拿到第6，但已比美國現任總統川普（Donald Trump）的17名好太多，連香港藝人劉德華都緊追在川普後面，拿下第18名。<br />\n<br />\nYouGov表示，中國領導人習近平與演員成龍，從2016年開始互換位置，去年習近平力壓成龍，但今年成龍又贏了習近平，應該是成龍的國際形象加分，儘管習近平是中國最受尊敬的人物，但成龍的全球影響力超越了習近平。<br />\n<br />\n女性方面，裘莉熱心公益形象深植人心，但前美國第一夫人、歐巴馬妻子蜜雪兒急起直追，分居1、2名；第3名則是美國名嘴歐普拉（Opreah Winfrey），硬把英國女王擠到第4名，也踩下了美國前國務卿希拉蕊。<br />\n<br />\n令人意外的是，不少中國女星進入前20大，包括劉亦菲、范冰冰、楊冪、趙薇等人。<br />\n<br />\n此次民調是針對全球35個國家、3萬7000多名受訪者進行的調查，是YouGov有史以來最大範圍的民調。調查分2階段，先問受訪者最欣賞哪位男人或女人？之後把得分最高的男女各選出前20人再請受訪者選出最欣賞者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-04-12/120579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2018-04-12%2F120579&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=de6daea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-04-12/120579</a>"},{"pid":"62831b569810e586b4ca0b1bc19b9c9d1037c6ac","tid":627526,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"大撚鑊, 成龍會唔會雜種鬥落黎?"},{"pid":"0dbe5c494978ddfd0a4e8b7e476a58ff20d0d79a","tid":627526,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大撚鑊, 成龍會唔會<span style=\"color: red;\">比</span>雜種鬥落黎?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7814abef6de420739d3eb21fa33e5931db66ed42","tid":627526,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"左膠榜又比奧巴馬兩公婆上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfb15d3228dc2d5585fd7af80a87ba2b32dc061","tid":627526,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"外國人識中國明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b272b7f505ad02ca73f4291d6b870bb3cd35b4","tid":627526,"uid":54270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"acfb15d3228dc2d5585fd7af80a87ba2b32dc061","tid":627526,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"外國人識中國明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"李小龍同成龍係功夫明星入面外國係頂級位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76f852735f4adb7f33a78def640319465b3effd","tid":627526,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acfb15d3228dc2d5585fd7af80a87ba2b32dc061","tid":627526,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"外國人識中國明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"識成龍唔奇 但係個topic 係尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劉亦菲、范冰冰、楊冪、趙薇 直頭識鬼你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a7d22bdc090ed32e8663022fa9a2fe5511cbb4","tid":627526,"uid":142604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f76f852735f4adb7f33a78def640319465b3effd","tid":627526,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acfb15d3228dc2d5585fd7af80a87ba2b32dc061","tid":627526,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"